```css

//learn more modal
.modal {
  display: none;
  width: 40%;
  margin: 0 auto;
  position: absolute;
  top: 200px;
  left: 50%;
  @include translateX(-50%);
  background: #fff;
  @include box-shadow;
  @include border-radius;
  overflow: hidden;
  .close-modal {
    position: absolute;
    right: 10px;
    top: 10px;
    color: #fff;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
  h2 {
    background: $blue;
    color: #fff;
    padding: 10px;
  }
  ul {
    padding: 10px 30px 30px 30px;
  }
}
```
